  "detailed_description": "Play as a robot with time-manipulating abilities. Travel to places you’ve never been by independently shifting back in time along the X and Y axes. But beware of pockets of corrupted space-time, and remember, tracking your positions through time consumes significant memory—without it, you won’t be able to function.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manipulating Space Time</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119950/extras/bae4d1a859293135735c6667834d020f.poster.avif?t=1738420590\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119950/extras/bae4d1a859293135735c6667834d020f.webm?t=1738420590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119950/extras/bae4d1a859293135735c6667834d020f.mp4?t=1738420590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Navigate puzzles keeping track of where you have been to reach places you could not reach before!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beware of Corrupted Space Time</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119950/extras/df3fed0f2a5e35d4ee5a010a42ff5648.poster.avif?t=1738420590\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119950/extras/df3fed0f2a5e35d4ee5a010a42ff5648.webm?t=1738420590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119950/extras/df3fed0f2a5e35d4ee5a010a42ff5648.mp4?t=1738420590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The straightest path is not always possible.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Limited Memory Capacity</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119950/extras/839e42ffc16c45e68ed43da3f21778a4.poster.avif?t=1738420590\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119950/extras/839e42ffc16c45e68ed43da3f21778a4.webm?t=1738420590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119950/extras/839e42ffc16c45e68ed43da3f21778a4.mp4?t=1738420590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Keep track of your memory available or you will over heat.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Editor</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119950/extras/ea26b90f9c4faf659c3445b0fd3186ef.poster.avif?t=1738420590\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119950/extras/ea26b90f9c4faf659c3445b0fd3186ef.webm?t=1738420590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119950/extras/ea26b90f9c4faf659c3445b0fd3186ef.mp4?t=1738420590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Make levels to share your creativity with others so we can all enjoy more puzzles together!",
